<figureCitation box="[1085,1154,766,793]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="4.[189,232,1919,1945]" captionTargetBox="[260,1327,1089,1876]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[249,1339,1083,1884]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Fig. 1. Map of the Philippines showing known distributions of Cyrtandra argentii Olivar, H.J.Atkins &amp; Muellner sp. nov. (*), C. ferruginea Merr. (■), C. hirtigera H.J.Atkins &amp; Cronk (◆), and C. villosissima Merr. (●) based on collection localities. A single point may represent more than one collection." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3928634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3928634/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
